title: IFeatureManager.EditRollback
description: Rolls back or forward the rollback bar to a specific location in the FeatureManager design tree.
signature:
System.Boolean EditRollback( 
   System.Int32
Location
,
   System.String
Feature
)

parameters.name: Location
parameters.description: Location to which to move the rollback bar as defined in swMoveRollbackBarTo_e

returns: True if moving the rollback bar back or forward was successful, false if not
remarks: When the model is in a rollback state, it reverts to an earlier state, suppressing recently added features. You can add new features or edit existing features while the model is in the rolled-back state.
